(30479, 501211, 'http://www.awfcarsaleshorsham.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>If you are looking for great savings on quality used cars in the Horsham area , then you have come to the right place. AWF Car Sales are a specialist used car dealer based in Southwater. We are proud to offer you a first class customer service and very competitive pricing, so please browse our stock list. We stock a range of used cars to suit all budgets and lifestyles with stock changing daily.</p>\r\n<p>If you are looking for a second hand car, then don''t delay, call us today to book a test drive. In order to offer cars to suit everyone we make sure that we update our stocklist regularly. It is therefore always worth giving us a call, even if you don''t see what you are looking for on our website.</p>\r\n<p>We realise that buying a car can be a daunting experience, but don''t worry, we are well established within the Southwater area and come with a great reputation. Furthermore we have huge experience and offer excellent advice on vehicles and vehicle maintenance. Our friendly staff will go the extra mile to guarantee that you receive the advice you need. This is the reason why many of our customers keep coming back to us.</p>\r\n<p>At AWF Car Sales we don''t just sell cars, we do everything possible to get you driving your perfect car so why not give us a call. We promise ''You''ll Love Buying Your Car From Us!''</p>', NULL, 'A W F Car Sales, Southwater, Horsham, RH12 3NS', 'AWF Car Sales are a specialist used car dealer based in Southwater.', '01403264004', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440062881, 1441614268, 'http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http://www.awfcarsaleshorsham.co.uk/', 'http://plus.google.com/share?url=http://www.awfcarsaleshorsham.co.uk/', 'http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=http://www.awfcarsaleshorsham.co.uk/', NULL, NULL, 'awf-car-sales', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30486, 501219, 'http://www.artepovera.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>What you find on my web site you won''t find anywhere else...and you won''t find it there twice.<br /><br />Unique, original, a one off is the all idea. Craftmanship is the result!</p>\r\n<p>I am a local artisan working from Worthing, West Sussex. I have being working as an artisan for some time now.</p>\r\n<p><br />I work with wood mostly and also very much enjoy finding reclaimed objects then restoring them to their former glory.<br /><br />All of my work is handmade and very rarely do I resort to ready made bits and pieces to speed up the creative process.<br /><br />I think doing what I do is great fun and enjoy the fact that most of my pieces are unique and every restoration is a discovery and preservation of the past.<br /><br />Thanks for visiting!!</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Vintage Restored Furniture & Handmade Home Decor', '07805998551', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440075315, 1440075964, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Arte-Povera', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/ArtePoveraCraft', NULL, NULL, 'arte-povera', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30453, 501181, 'www.axlr8cars.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We have over 50 years experience buying and selling quality used vehicles..<br />when you visit us we will only offer you the information you need to know. we will not pressurise you just leave you to make up your own mind in your own time. We will not offer to sell you products that are purely profit based .There is nothing worse than a hungry salesman!<br />All cars over &pound;2000 have a comprehensive Autoprotect 3 month warranty included in the forecourt price with an option to upgrade to 12 or 24 months.All our cars have been HPi checked.</p>', NULL, 'AXLR8 Cars, North Farm Road, Tunbridge Wells. Kent. TN2 3BW', 'Welcome to AXLR8. We are a used car dealership based in Royal Tunbridge Wells, KENT.', '01892544446', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439887424, 1441613233, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'axlr8', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
