(48553, 502423, 'http://www.drabtofabfurniture.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We have Rustic &amp; aged furniture that has a natural Shabby Chic look, we also stock 40/50&rsquo;s &amp; Retro 60&rsquo;s &amp; 70&rsquo;s furniture, our stock changes daily so keep an eye on the website.</p>\r\n<p>We also have a selection of hand painted up cycled furniture, giving it a new lease of life and making it look wonderful again using Annie Sloan&rsquo;s environmentally friendly chalk paints, our painted furniture is then waxed with Annie Sloan waxes to protect.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Welcome to Drab To Fab Furniture we specialise in a wide range of top quality used Pine,Oak, Retro & Painted Furniture', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440594059, 1440594438, 'https://www.facebook.com/fromdrabtofab', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'drab-to-fab-furniture', 'uploads/usersite/48501_48600', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30434, 501156, 'http://www.elitecarsuk.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p class="justify">At Elite Cars we pride ourselves in presenting our cars to the highest of standards. We offer all main dealer facilities, without the inflated showroom prices. We endeavour to be the lowest priced used car sales centre, offering the best cars at the best prices.</p>\r\n<p class="justify">With over 20 years of experience in the motor trade you can be sure that we will be able to advise you on the many different aspects of a vehicle purchase whether you have seen a vehicle in our stock, want knowledge of model specifications, details of finance packages or if you know what you want and would like us to source your ideal car for you. As an independent dealer we can offer all this and more with a friendly and personal service.</p>\r\n<p class="justify">We offer various finance packages that we can tailor to your needs. All the finance packages are at the most competitive rates available.</p>\r\n<p class="justify">We specialise in 4x4&rsquo;s, 4x4 7 Seater&rsquo;s, MPV&rsquo;s, and People Carriers in both Diesel and Petrol forms. We also sell other types of cars from convertibles, sport coupe&rsquo;s, super cars, small hatchbacks, medium saloons to vans. Makes include &ndash; ASTON MARTIN, AUDI, BMW, BENTLEY, CHEVOLET, FORD, HONDA, HYUNDAI, JAGUAR, KIA, LAND ROVER, MAZDA, MERCEDES, MITSUBISHI, NISSAN, PEUGEOT, SKODA, SUBARU, SUZUKI, TOYOTA, VAUXHALL, VW AND VOLVO to name a few makes.</p>\r\n<p class="justify">Come and see us and we are confident you will appreciate our honest and customer service led environment.</p>', NULL, 'Market House, 2 Marlborough Road, Swindon, Wiltshire, SN3 1QY', 'Welcome to Elite Cars based in Swindon, Wiltshire. We are conveniently located just 5 minutes from junction 15 or 16 on the M4 Motorway.', '01793698498', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439800238, 1440147236, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'elite-cars', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
