(48475, 502265, 'http://www.esl-ltd.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<div style="color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12.8000001907349px;">\r\n<p>For over 20 years, we at ESL have been involved in commercial soft landscaping right across the South East, spanning as far north as Peterborough and as far west as Bristol.</p>\r\n<p>We pride ourselves in completing landscape schemes for a wide variety of clients, including company headquarters, new schools and academies, business and retail parks, superstores and industrial estates, as well as involving ourselves in ecologically sensitive areas.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Popular Services</strong></p>\r\n<p><em>Soft Landscaping</em></p>\r\n<p>ESL Landscape Contractors has a vast experience in soft landscaping, starting with pricing from drawings, to site visits in order to ensure the most competitive quote, whilst working closely with the landscape architects and client.</p>\r\n<p><em>Fencing</em></p>\r\n<p>ESL can carry out a wide range of fencing requirements. Wooden panels / trellis / picket fencing and metal fencing. Bespoke fencing can be undertaken for all individual fencing needs. All types of fencing supplied and installed.</p>\r\n<p><em>Maintenance</em></p>\r\n<p>Our maintenance includes services such as strimming and spraying of sites, which ensures your project looks, and stays, as healthy and aesthetic as we intended.</p>\r\n<p><em>Private Dwellings</em></p>\r\n<p>ESL carry out a full service for private gardens from clearance work through to the final planting&nbsp;All types of fencing supplied and installed.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>', 1, 'Orpington, Orpington', NULL, '01689326862', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440407484, 1442486132, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'esl-landscape-contractors-doWll6iF', 'uploads/usersite/48401_48500', 606, 0, '5QBJZPSBQ'),
