(30409, 501118, 'www.saxton4x4.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Based in the city of Chelmsford, Essex, we are proud to be an official Overfinch and Onyx centre offering a diverse range of expertly modified 4x4s and specialist cars. Our state of the art showroom, the largest of its kind in the UK scaling over 100,000 square foot houses more than five hundred premium 4x4s over two floors all under cover, so whatever the weather you can view our vehicles all year round. You will find the most prestigious 4x4s handpicked from the likes of Land Rover, Porsche, Audi, BMW, Mercedes-Benz, Lexus, Volvo, Volkswagen and many more all under one roof.</p>\r\n<p>Browse our comprehensive line-up of models in our climate-controlled, mood-lit and relaxed environment with access to all areas provided by our bespoke fully-glazed scenic lift and expansive walkways. Take advantage of all the creature comforts on offer; such as our specialist coffee bar serving hot and cold refreshments to enjoy from our executive lounge and panoramic viewing area overlooking our boutique showroom. Families are also catered for through our specified children&rsquo;s play area fully stocked with games consoles, board games, and various books, so the kids can enjoy themselves while you hunt for your dream 4x4.</p>\r\n<p>Our multi-purpose site also features a sixteen-bay service paddock using the latest diagnostic equipment. Relax in our service reception offering a coffee bar and a viewing area to see all the work taking place by our fully-trained and experienced technicians. Every vehicle is professionally valeted and detailed by our expert team to ensure the highest finish on our vehicles. When your car is ready you can collect it from our designated handover bay from one of our knowledgeable Business Managers who are there at every stage to answer your questions. Find directions to our modern showroom on our contact us page or get in touch on to speak to one of our friendly team on 01245 351234 today.</p>', NULL, 'Westway Chelmsford Essex CM1 3BH', 'Saxton 4x4 is the UK’s number one independent 4x4 dealership having been trading in the world’s leading marques for over forty years.', '01245351234', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439456650, 1440492018, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/100890867649789319382/videos?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'saxton-4x4', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
