(30469, 501201, 'http://www.alljapanesemotors.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Why buy a car from Japan?</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Excellent high specification exciting models that are not otherwise available in the UK.</li>\r\n<li>Superior condition than the UK equivalent of the same age.</li>\r\n<li>No salt is used on the roads in Japan leaving the chassis (underneath of the car) corrosion (rust) free</li>\r\n<li>In Japan they have a very strict test every 2 years equivalent to a worthiness certificate that can cost up to &pound; 2000 a time.</li>\r\n<li>The Japanese take pride in their vehicles and invariably keep them in good condition not only for their respect for their vehicles but in anticipation for the test.</li>\r\n</ul>', NULL, 'KV Cars Ltd, 1 Rooth Street, Stockport. SK4 1DJ', 'Welcome to All Japanese Motors. The Japanese vehicle import specialists for over 13 years.', '01614807559', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440059284, 1440663401, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/109105000473105495084/about?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'all-japanese-motors', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
