(30374, 501069, 'http://www.trojancars.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>With nearly 30 years of new and used car experience in the Portsmouth area we are able to source high quality used vehicles presented to the highest standards. All of our vehicles and items for sale are hand-picked and offered at very keen prices. How do we achieve this? Our knowledge of the market, trade contacts and use of the internet means we can pass on our savings in the form of very competitive prices.<br /><br />We also specialise in classic cars, motorcycles and scooters, primarily 1950&rsquo;s and 1960&rsquo;s English and American; and especially classic British &lsquo;Rock &amp; Roll&rsquo; cars! Plus, we are always on the look out for interesting collectibles, especially motoring memorabilia, toys, jukeboxes and other items of interest.<br /><br />Please browse our pages and contact us by telephone or e-mail if you would like to discuss any of the items on display, or have similar items that you think we might be interested to buy.<br /><br />We are always looking to purchase or part exchange similar quality vehicles or items with cash either way.<br /><br />Please contact us to arrange viewing.<br /><br />Thank you</p>', NULL, '245–247 Francis Avenue, Southsea. Hampshire. PO4 0AL', 'Trojan Cars specialise cheap used cars | Finance | Warranty | Portsmouth and Portsmouth and Southsea Hampshire UK in pre-owned family, sports and prestige autom', '02392299080', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439195585, 1440492785, 'https://www.facebook.com/TrojanCars?sk=app_175456335854933', 'https://plus.google.com/112766815547566255020/videos?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/TrojanCars', NULL, NULL, 'trojan-car-sales', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
