(48199, -3301735, 'http://www.olympicplumbers.com/', 'uploads/company/-3304999_-3300000', '<p>When it comes to gas in your home, you need to ensure your home and family are protected. Checking your gas appliances and pipework could save the lives of you and your loved ones.</p>\r\n<p>Our fully trained engineers are on hand to conduct gas safety checks for your home or business in South London.</p>\r\n<p>Olympic Plumbers are on hand to provide a comprehensive emergency 24 hour service in the Waterloo, Clapham, Westminster and South London area.</p>\r\n<p>From dripping taps to installations, we are experienced in all aspects of plumbing,so if you need the professional touch, we''re here for you.</p>\r\n<p>Installing your new appliances can often be a daunting experience. Make sure your new appliance is installed correctly by calling in Olympic Plumbers.</p>\r\n<p>Our specialist team will ensure your appliance is installed correctly, leaving you to enjoy your appliance safe in the knowledge everything is as it should be.</p>\r\n<p><br /><br /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 1, 'Waterloo, London', NULL, '02073510000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440407105, 1442483942, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'olympic-plumbers', 'uploads/usersite/48101_48200', 618, 0, 'KFAWISCFM'),
