(48507, 502309, 'http://www.Raystede.org/events', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: 12pt; font-family: times new roman, serif;"><span style="font-family: calibri, sans-serif; color: #1f497d;">Raystede&nbsp;Centre for Animal Welfare&nbsp;Boot&nbsp;Fairs, raising money to support the animals in our care.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: 12pt; font-family: times new roman, serif;"><span style="font-family: calibri, sans-serif; color: #1f497d;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: 12pt; font-family: times new roman, serif;"><span style="font-family: calibri, sans-serif; color: #808285; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;">At&nbsp;Raystede&nbsp;we are passionate about the wellbeing of all animals and are committed to giving them the best possible life.&nbsp; We rescue, rehome and provide sanctuary for more than 1500 animals each year. Located on the&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: calibri, sans-serif; color: #1f497d;">Broyle near Ringmer.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: calibri, sans-serif; color: #808285; background-image: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Our Sanctuary, with its sizeable lakes, offers a safe haven for visiting waterfowl as well as for our chickens, turkeys, ducks and geese. We also offer a lifelong home for goats, horses, ponies and donkeys which are no longer wanted. Visit our shop &amp; Cafe and see our animals.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-size: 12pt; font-family: times new roman, serif;"><span style="font-family: calibri, sans-serif; color: #1f497d;">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; color: #222222; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><font color="#1f497d" face="Calibri, sans-serif">BOOTFAIRS &nbs