(30475, 501207, 'http://www.dinnages.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>You will find your local Dinnages car dealership in East and West Sussex conveniently located in <strong>Haywards Heath</strong>, <strong>Burgess Hill</strong>, <strong>Worthing</strong> and <strong>Brighton</strong>, where we offer a wide range of unbeatable car deals.</p>\r\n<p>At Dinnages, we offer the entire range of new Ford cars, new commercial vehicles, new Volvo cars and a selection of high quality used cars in Sussex, all at unbeatable prices. Our selection of Ford offers and Volvo offers are updated regularly to offer you fantastic savings across our range of new and used cars, as well as servicing and aftersales in Sussex.</p>\r\n<p>Take a look at our offers pages for the latest deals available and contact us for further information.</p>\r\n<p>Locations:</p>\r\n<p><strong>Haywards Heath</strong> - Ford Dealer and Renault Aftersales. <br /><strong>Burgess Hill</strong> - Ford Dealer.<br /><strong>Brighton</strong> - Ford Dealer and Transit Centre. <br /><strong>Worthing</strong> - Ford Dealer and Volvo Dealer.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'Dinnages Car Dealers in Sussex are proud to represent Ford, Ford Commercial and Volvo across the county.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440061408, 1441798830, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Dinnages-Worthing-Haywards-Heath-Burgess-Hill-Brighton/10666269273235', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/DinnagesGarages', NULL, NULL, 'dinnages', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30398, 501104, 'http://www.garageonthegreen.com', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We are pleased to always have on for sale between 40 and 50 quality used cars based in St Leonards on Sea near Hastings for you to look at at your leisure.</p>\r\n<p>We have been in business for over 20 years and in that time we have built up many friendly contacts in the local motor trade enabling us to source quality used cars at the best prices. If you know the car you want and we don&rsquo;t have it in stock we&rsquo;ll aim to source it for you.</p>\r\n<p>Many of our customers, both local and national return to us again and again as they are impressed with the level of service received and they often recommend us to friends and family.</p>\r\n<p>Your current car can be used as full deposit on any one of our quality used cars and a finance deal, if required, can be tailored to suit every pocket.</p>\r\n<p>Your new car will come &lsquo;as standard&rsquo; with a full HPI check, new MOT, 6 month warranty, with options to extend for up to three years at an additional cost, and a service as required.</p>', NULL, NULL, 'If you are looking for the best second hand cars for sale in St Leonards on Sea and Hastings in East Sussex, you have come to the right place!', '01424718080', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439369876, 1441371905, 'https://www.facebook.com/GarageOnTheGreen', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/GarageGreen', NULL, NULL, 'garage-on-the-green', 'uploads/usersite/30301_30400', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30431, 501153, 'http://www.gmacommercials.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>We are an established truck and van centre near Eastbourne with over 19 years experience.We supply a range of new &amp; used vehicles at very affordable prices &amp; specialise in 1 owner vehicles.<br /><br />We are situated along the A22 at Lower Dicker adjacent to the willow cafe and are just 1 mile from the main town of Hailsham which has main line train stations nearby where we provide transport to &amp; from for customers.We are within an hours drive from London and just a short drive from anywhere in Kent, Sussex and Surrey.We also have a site atSwanley Kent 1 mile from Jct 3 M25 where we stock a range of 12ton+ HGV''s.<br /><br />Our experienced sales team give good advise to help choose the right vehicle for you.We have a selection of finance options in place to get you the best deal.We can also arrange delivery of your commercial vehicle to anywhere within the UK and make regular deliveries to all major ports for export.We pride ourselves on our good quality service and good quality commercials which make GMA Commercials the only choice to make.</p>', NULL, 'GMA Commercials A22 Lower Dicker  Hailsham East Sussex BN27 4BT', 'Welcome to GMA Commercials, Used Van and Truck Dealer in Hailsham near Eastbourne East Sussex.', '01323441090', '07831104419', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439799724, 1440490993, 'https://www.facebook.com/GMACommercials?sk=app_175456335854933', 'https://plus.google.com/104084479951623441557/about?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/GMACOMMERCIALS', NULL, NULL, 'gma-commercials', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30419, 501136, 'http://www.idealcommercials.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>With years of combined experience in the motor trade, we are able to advise you on the most suitable vehicle for your business needs. We can source and supply quality used commercials vans and used vehicles at affordable prices to Hampshire, East Sussex, West Sussex, Berkshire and anywhere else in the UK. Please view our stock list page to see our latest selection of used vans for sale. Whether its Large Vans, Medium Vans, Small Vans, 4x4,Trucks or Tippers your looking for, Ideal Commercials can cater for your every need. We look forward to speaking to you soon</p>', NULL, 'Ideal Commercials Ltd Warnford Road West Meon Petersfield Hampshire GU32 1JN', 'Welcome to Ideal Commercials Ltd', '01730829080', '07768197225', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439542419, 1440492202, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Ideal-Commercials/231961333554878?sk=app_175456335854933', 'https://plus.google.com/107175583707627680423/about?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/idealcommercial', NULL, NULL, 'ideal-commercials-ltd', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30100, -26877, 'http://www.jcleisure.co.uk', 'uploads/company/-29999_-25000', '<p>Welcome to JC Leisure - Winchelsea East Sussex.<br /> <br /> Used Motorhomes and Campervans for sale in Winchelsea East Sussex.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Great selection of Campervans in Sussex and Kent.</span><br /> <br /> We have a good selection of used motorhomes for sale, stock changes regularly. Prices from &pound;5,000 to &pound;30,000, whether you are looking for a large 6 berth coachbuilt, or a small camper, Mercedes or Swift we may have the one for you.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Easy Access from London and the Home Counties.</span><br /> <br /> We are 1 hour from Dartford Tunnel<br /> <br /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Nearly New &amp; Used Motorhomes.<br /> <br /> </span>Browse through our up to date stocklist, or please speak or email our friendly team. We offer one year motorhome warranty and MOT, plus 6m Road Tax with every used motorhome.<br /> <br /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Our Pre Delivery Service.<br /> <br /> </span>All used motorhomes have following checks in our specialised motorhome workshops<br /> Habitation check inc gas/equipment check<br /> Mechanical service inc cambelt change<br /> New Gas Hose/Regulator<br /> Full Valet<br /> Full Demonstration<br /> <br /> Finance and Part Exchange Welcome<br /> <br /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Accessory Shop.<br /> <br /> </span>Spares Shop<br /> Gaz and Calor Gas<br /> Bike Racks and Awnings Supplied and Fitted<br /> <br /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Motorhome and Campervan accident repair</span>.<br /> <br /> Insurance estimates for all bodywork inc internal repairs<br /> Damp checks<br /> <br /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Motorhome workshop.<br /> <br /> </span>Habitation checks<br /> Motorhome mechanical servicing<br /> <br /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Selling a Motorhome or Camper</span>.<br /> <br /> Ring Dave for our best price</p>', 1