(30445, 501168, 'www.karhouse.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Quality used cars &amp; a friendly service</p>\r\n<p>Karhouse independent used car specialist, based in Chesham, Buckinghamshire.</p>\r\n<p>We know about used cars, so look no further than Karhouse and ring us today for friendly and honest advice.</p>\r\n<p>Our services include Used Car sales, Service, Repairs, Storage,&nbsp;Warranty &amp; Finance.</p>', NULL, 'Karhouse, Bellingdon Road. Chesham. Buckinghamshire. HP5 2NN', 'Welcome to Karhouse', '01494958607', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439803071, 1441181498, 'http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=', 'https://plus.google.com/share?url=', 'http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=', NULL, NULL, 'karhouse', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30473, 501205, 'http://www.mccarthycars.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>McCarthy Cars, a Family Run Business established Over 40 Years ago, pride ourselves on our Customer Service and Satisfaction that&rsquo;s why we were voted Croydon''s Most Loved Business 2013, UK&rsquo;s Most Loved Car Dealership 2012 and 2013, Most Loved Business in Croydon and Second Most Loved Car Dealership in the UK 2011 and Finalists in the 2010, 2011 and 2012 Motor Trader Awards, and Finalists in the 2012 AM Awards, and Winners of the Car Dealer Customer Care Award 2012, 2013 and 2014. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>We take great pride in the reputation that we have achieved, a reputation that has been earned by selling high quality used cars in london, always presented to the very highest possible standard and backed up by the most comprehensive after sales service found anywhere.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="defaultparagraphstyle11">You will always be greeted by our friendly and knowledgeable sales staff, who are only too happy to assist in anyway that they can to make purchasing a car an easy and enjoyable experience.&nbsp;Our aim is not to sell you just one used car, but to sell you used cars for the rest of your life and to become friends. We realise that to achieve this aim, you must be satisfied with your car and, more importantly, we know that we must gain your trust and respect.</p>\r\n<p class="defaultparagraphstyle11">Winners of Used Car Retailer of the Year in the 2013 Motor Trader Awards</p>\r\n<p>Winners of Best Customer Care Award in the 2012, 2013 and 2014 CarDealer Used Car Awards</p>', NULL, 'McCarthy Cars, 72-74 Mitcham Road, Croydon. Surrey. CR0 3RG', 'McCarthy Cars is a award winning, approved used car dealer located in Croydon.', '02086888086', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440060630, 1441614573, 'https://www.facebook.com/McCarthyCars', 'https://plus.google.com/101682779386882410186/about?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/mccarthycarsuk', NULL, NULL, 'mccarthy-cars', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30415, 501132, 'http://www.lmwmotors.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>New Barn Motor Company was established in 1996 and specialises in buying and selling pre-owned cars, mini buses and light commercial vehicles.</p>\r\n<p>Founded by Nick Hardaker, following 25 years of motor trade and finance experience, New Barn Motor Company has established itself as a leading independent vehicle retailer in East Sussex.</p>\r\n<p>Originally based in Horam, East Sussex, where we still have a presence, we offer friendly, honest advice and competitive prices to ensure you get the best deal available. All our cars, mini buses and light commercial vehicles are selected to ensure you buy a quality vehicle with confidence.</p>\r\n<p>New Barn Motor Company works in partnership with LMW Motors Ltd which was established in 1992 by Leigh Field, and offer complete workshop facilities for servicing, repairs, parts, tyres, batteries and MOT&rsquo;s. Whilst specialising in Audi, BMW and Volkswagen, LMW Motors Ltd is staffed by highly experienced technicians, and equipped with the latest computerised diagnostic and test equipment and as such is able to undertake service and repair work on any make of vehicle. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', NULL, 'New Barn Motor Co Westham Service Station Eastbourne Road  Eastbourne, Westham East Sussex BN24 5NE', 'Used Cars in Eastbourne East Sussex | Car Dealers Eastbourne East Sussex', '01323769988', '07956833132', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439540706, 1440493310, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'new-barn-motor-company-nbmc-lmw', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30478, 501210, 'http://www.northstarpremier.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>orth Star Premier Ltd was established in 2004 to cover both East Sussex and West Sussex. Conveniently located in central Portslade, just off the Old Shoreham Road, within sight of Portslade train station and on many bus routes. <br /><br />Here at Northstar Premier we stock at least 30 quality used cars. We believe in providing the best vehicles, treating people fairly, building long term relationships and giving you the best deal. We offer used cars at discounted prices beating the franchised car dealerships on both service and price. As Licensed Credit Brokers we offer competitive loan facilities to all, including finance settlements and debt counseling. Part exchange facilities are available.<br /><br />We are well known in the Brighton area and we have over 40 years experience in all aspects of the motor trade. Using this we aim to make buying a car a pleasure with the reassurance that you are buying from experienced and friendly people with a professional approach.<br /><br />We are pleased to offer the majority of our cars as low mileage, one owner with full service history and are HPI cleared and RAC guaranteed. This can be extended up to 2 years.<br /><br />We can offer you a quote to buy or contract using HP, finance, lease, contract hire, lease purchase.</p>', NULL, 'North Star Premier, 20 Carlton Terrace, Portslade. East Sussex. BN41 1XF', 'Welcome to North Star Premier in Brighton, Sussex. Perfectly situated in Portslade to supply used Cars and Vans in East and West Sussex.', '01273415100', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440062814, 1441184141, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/115462854345614263674/about?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'north-star-premier', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30476, 501208, 'http://www.northstarsussex.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>All of our cars are carefully selected from trusted sources by one of our directors and then inspected in one of our workshops and road tested before being valeted and prepared for retail sale. When sold the vehicles are then serviced, Mot&rsquo;d if necessary and supplied with our own comprehensive 3 month guarantee that, in the unlikely event of a problem, includes recovery and the use of a replacement car. This combined with our meticulous preparation and extensive guarantee ensures total peace of mind. It is the intention of the North Star Sussex not only to sell our customers a first class used car but to be able to cater for all their ongoing motoring needs. North Star Sussex is situated on the old A 23 London to Brighton road at Sayers Common, which is 6 miles north of Brighton near the Hickstead All England Show Jumping ground. The company operates from spacious premises that afford plenty of room for the display of sales vehicles and easy customer parking, we specialise in the sale of nearly new, low mileage, top quality used cars at the most competitive, no haggle, prices. There is normally a choice of up to 100 cars available for sale at Sayers Common Sussex. We also stock a selection of vans and light commercial vehicles.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Every North Star customer receives the personal attention of the staff and our directors as it is our aim to build an ongoing business relationship. We pride ourselves on the number of our customers who converse with us on first name terms, recommend us to their family and friends, return to us for all their motoring requirements and become our friends.</p>', NULL, 'North Star Sayers Common, London Road, Sayers Common, Hassocks. West Sussex. BN6 9HZ', 'North Star Motor Group are trustworthy Car and Van dealers who offer used vehicles at discounted prices.', '01273832400', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440062335, 1441184654, 'https://www.facebook.com/NorthStarSussex?fref=ts', 'https://plus.google.com/108456733648080837957/about?hl=en', 'https://twitter.com/NorthStarSussex', NULL, NULL, 'north-star-sussex', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(48554, 502425, 'http://www.shfurnishings.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>At Southern Home Furnishings we want to offer you the best quality products at competitive prices. We work closely with our manufacturers to ensure that what you are ordering is everything you expect it to be and more</p>', NULL, '5 - 6 True Blue Presinct, Wick Street, BN17 7JN Littlehampton', 'We offer a wide collection of home furnishings for all aspects of your home, from lounge and dining to bedroom and outdoor living', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440603220, 1440603614, 'https://www.facebook.com/shfurnishings', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'southern-home-furnishings', 'uploads/usersite/48501_48600', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30406, 501115, 'http://www.skinnersnet.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Skinners of Rye are situated in the ancient historic market town of Rye, East Sussex, close to the Kent and Sussex borders and a short distance from Hastings. Skinners of Rye have been supplying and servicing all makes of Cars and Commercial Vehicles to Kent and the South East for over 100 years.<br /><br />We carry a comprehensive selection of quality used cars in stock covering all makes and models. This ranges from small economical super minis &amp; hatchbacks with petrol or diesel engines, sports cars and luxury saloons, through to 4 Wheel Drive Off Road, SUV and Commercial Vehicles.</p>', NULL, 'Skinners of Rye 74 Fishmarket Road  Rye East Sussex TN31 7LP', 'Used Cars in Hastings, Ashford, Rye & Tunbridge Wells, East Sussex', '01797223334', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439456132, 1441270957, 'https://www.facebook.com/SkinnersofRye', 'https://plus.google.com/u/0/103418899576257388256/videos', 'https://twitter.com/SkinnersRye', NULL, NULL, 'skinners-of-rye', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30444, 501167, 'http://www.southdownscarsales.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>South Downs Car Sales Ltd are the friendliest used car dealer in Sussex. Our cars are all low mileage, with one or two owners from new, a full service history and are all HPI checked clear. Our site is perfectly positioned here in mid-Sussex with easy access to both the A23 &amp; A27 carriageways, we neighbour Hassocks train station which is on the London to Brighton train line.</p>\r\n<p>We hand pick only the very best used cars for our site, this combined with over 50 years of combined experience in the motor industry and a market leading RAC Warranty scheme helps to ensure that our customer''s satisfaction remains our top priority.</p>\r\n<p>As an established used car dealer serving Sussex we offer part exchange, very competitive finance packages, GAP insurance and extendable warranties.</p>\r\n<p>As we complete our 5th successful year of business we have further extended our stock to over 100 quality pre-owned vehicles for customers to choose from. We continue to be proud members of the most respected Buy With Confidence accreditation from the West Sussex County Council''s Trading Standards Department. Such achievements along with our staff''s friendly manner and knowledgeable advice will ensure that we maintain and further strengthen our position as the number one in the South!!</p>', NULL, 'South Downs Car Sales Ltd Station Business Park Keymer Road Hassocks, Nr Brighton West Sussex BN6 8JA', 'Welcome to South Downs Car Sales Ltd', '01273846884', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439803061, 1441183240, 'https://www.facebook.com/SouthDownCarSales', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/SouthDownsCars', NULL, NULL, 'south-downs-car-sales-ltd', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30450, 501178, 'http://www.strattoncarcompany.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Based in the village of Nutley East Sussex, just a few minutes from Uckfield, with Crowborough, Tunbridge Wells, Haywards Heath, Eastbourne, Burgess Hill, Brighton, Crawley and Gatwick in close proximity, easily accessible via the M25 and M23 near East Grinstead.<br /><br />We are a family run independent used car retailer and our primary concern is your safety, as a result we specialise in the sale of quality, previously owned vehicles hand picked by ourselves and prepared to the very highest of standards.<br /><br />Whatever your requirements may be our aim is to provide the highest level of customer satisfaction, you can be sure of a warm welcome accompanied by a friendly professional team with no hard sell, ultimately delivering a smooth and pleasant buying experience.</p>', NULL, 'Stratton Car Company London Road Horney Common Nutley East Sussex TN22 3EA', 'Used Cars in Nutley Nr Uckfield, East Sussex\r\n\r\nUsed Cars For Sale at Stratton Car Company Nutley Nr Uckfield', '01825729190', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439886274, 1441270805, 'https://www.facebook.com/StrattonCarCompany', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/strattoncarcomp', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VNUA0qKGNuQ', 'stratton-car-company', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
