(30438, 501160, 'www.dorsetvehiclesales.co.uk', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Dorset Vehicle Rentals is one of the largest Independent Vehicle Rental Companies in the South West, priding itself on excellent customer service - making sure our customers come back to use us time and time again.</p>\r\n<p>We are now pleased to offer MotoNovo Finance, offering competitive car and commercial vehicle finance. Ask for a quotation, that can be tailored to meet your own needs. Thus giving you the chance to buy the vehicle of your choice - that you thought you couldn''t afford!</p>\r\n<p>If you would like further information about the vehicles listed please feel free to telephone Andrew Wright our Vehicle Sales Manager on 08000 46 78 78 or mobile 07815 897 615 <br />&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Services available:-<br />Ex Fleet Used Vehicle Sales, Finance, Part Exchange, Warranty.</p>\r\n<p>Authorised and Regulated by the Financial Conduct Authority.</p>', NULL, 'Dorset Vehicle Sales, Upwey Service Station, 727 Dorchester Road. Weymouth. Dorset. DT3 5LF', 'Dorset Vehicle Sales is a division of Dorset Vehicle Rentals. Established back in 1995 in Dorset, and gradually expanded out into Somerset in recent years.', '01305814111', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439801463, 1440147088, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'dorset-vehicle-sales', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30402, 501111, 'http://www.auto-sportiva.com/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p class="margin-top">Based in <strong>Sevenoaks</strong> we specialise in all makes of prestige cars including <strong>Audi, BMW, Landrover, Mercedes-Benz,Volkswagen, Lexus, Honda, Mazda, Porsche, Lotus and Kia.</strong></p>\r\n<p class="margin-top"><strong>Why are we the "definitive"?</strong></p>\r\n<p>We only offer the best choice of prestige cars in the UK and are able to offer servicing repairs, maintenance and professional valeting to all of our customer&rsquo;s.</p>\r\n<p>We have access to fully trained mechanics with vast experience on a variety of brands able to help with any customer queries or issues.</p>\r\n<p>We source the majority of our cars from the main dealer network (having previously worked within it), from private owners or from our existing data base.</p>\r\n<p>As we are a small business and not hindered by the huge overheads Franchise dealers are faced with, we offer vastly competitive rates when it comes to servicing and repairs.</p>\r\n<p>Will (Director) and Guy (Sales Manager), like all our customers are car enthusiasts. Customer service is paramount, not only at the point of sale but throughout the entire ownership period. Giving our customers the "total customer experience" is our priority.</p>\r\n<p>We believe that there is no reason to go anywhere else for your Prestige car needs, our cars are prepared to the highest standards and come with comprehensive warranties.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>So if it&rsquo;s a Sports and Prestige car your interested in please pay us a visit and have a coffee or give us a call for a free and informative chat, we look forward to seeing you!</p>', NULL, 'Birchwood Garage, 116 London Road, Sevenoaks. Kent. TN13 1BH', 'WELCOME TO AUTO-SPORTIVA\r\n\r\nCongratulations you have found the definitive home for pre-owned Sports and Prestige Cars in the UK!', '01732 450731', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1439454650, 1441613729, 'https://www.facebook.com/pages/Auto-Sportiva/411609635615153', NULL, 'https://twitter.com/search?q=AutoSportiva1', NULL, NULL, 'auto-sportiva', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL),
(30471, 501203, 'http://www.goldsmithandallcorn.co.uk/', 'uploads/company/500001_505000', '<p>Goldsmith &amp; Allcorn ensure you can buy with confidence as all our vehicles come with a minimum 12 month warranty.</p>\r\n<p>Goldsmith and Allcorn are a Vauxhall main agent, selling all New Vauxhall cars, Agila, Adam, Corsa, Meriva, Astra, Zafira Tourer, Insignia, Cascada, Mokka and Antara as well as commercial vehicles, Corsa, Combo, Vivaro and Movano.</p>\r\n<p>We also service all Vauxhalls and other makes at competitive prices serving the towns of Heathfield, Uckfield, Crowborough, Lewes, Newhaven, Peacehaven, Brighton, Hove, Hailsham, Battle, Etchingham, East Grinstead and Haywards Heath.</p>', NULL, 'Goldsmith and Allcorn, Bell Lane, Uckfield. East Sussex. TN22 1QL', 'Goldsmith & Allcorn have been in business for over 35 years and always try to treat customers as we would like to be treated.', '01435865858', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1440060073, 1440663815, NULL, 'https://plus.google.com/113541561918179039041/about?hl=en', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'goldsmith-allcorn', 'uploads/usersite/30401_30500', NULL, 0, NULL);
